quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  7,79,"Nígbà náà, (Sọ̄lih) ṣẹ́rí kúrò lọ́dọ̀ wọn, ó sì sọ pé: “Ẹ̀yin ìjọ mi, mo kúkú ti jẹ́ iṣẹ́ Olúwa mi fún yín. Mo sì ti fún yín ní ìmọ̀ràn rere ṣùgbọ́n ẹ̀yin kò fẹ́ràn àwọn onímọ̀ràn rere.”"
  7,80,"(Rántí Ànábì) Lūt, nígbà tí ó sọ fún ìjọ rẹ̀ pé: “Ṣé ẹ óò máa ṣe ìbàjẹ́ ni tí kò sí ẹnì kan nínú àwọn ẹ̀dá tó ṣe irú rẹ̀ rí?"
  7,81,"Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin (ọkùnrin) ń lọ jẹ adùn (ìbálòpọ̀) lára àwọn ọkùnrin (ẹgbẹ́ yín) dípò àwọn obìnrin! Àní sẹ́, ìjọ alákọyọ ni yín.”"
  8,13,"Ìyẹn nítorí pé, wọ́n yapa (ọ̀rọ̀) Allāhu àti Òjíṣẹ́ Rẹ̀. Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá sì yapa (ọ̀rọ̀) Allāhu àti Òjíṣẹ́ Rẹ̀, dájúdájú Allāhu le (níbi) ìyà."
  8,14,"Ìyẹn (ni ìyà tayé). Nítorí náà, ẹ tọ́ ọ wò. Àti pé dájúdájú ìyà Iná ń bẹ fún àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́."
  8,15,"Ẹ̀yin tí ẹ gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, nígbà tí ẹ bá pàdé àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́, tí wọ́n ń wọ́ jáde níkọ̀ níkọ̀, ẹ̀yin kò gbọdọ̀ pẹ̀yìn dà sí wọn (láti ságun)."